import {gql} from 'apollo-server'

export default gql `
    type User{
        id:String!
        name:String!
        email:String!
        createdAt:String!
        updateAt:String!
        bio: String
        avatar: String
        sayings(take:Int!,lastId:Int): [Saying]
        tags:[Tag]
    }

`;

import { gql } from "apollo-server";

export default gql`
type Saying{
    id: Int!
    user: User!
    author:Author!
    createdAt:String!
    updateAt:String!
    tags: [Tag]
    text:String!
    totalLikes:Int!
    totalComments:Int!
    isMine: Boolean!
    isLike: Boolean!
}
type Like{
    id:Int!
    saying: Saying!
    createdAt:String!
    updateAt:String!

}


`;
//  Tag  Saying
//  Tag  Saying
